# __PROJECT_NAME__ - Cursor entry pointer

The single source of project conventions is `AGENTS.md`.
The scoped, auto-loaded rules live in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.
The persistent Claude Code memory is in `CLAUDE.md`.

Do NOT add rules here. This file is kept intentionally thin so Cursor's
modern `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` system owns rule scoping via `globs` and
`alwaysApply`. Adding content here duplicates context and burns tokens.

If you were about to edit this file, edit `AGENTS.md` or create a new
`.cursor/rules/NNN-*.mdc` instead.
